data.title: Associated Press News: Breaking News, Latest Headlines and Videos
data.meta_description: Read the latest headlines, breaking news, and videos at APNews.com, the definitive source for independent journalism from every corner of the globe.
data.text:
Democratic presidential nominee Vice President Kamala Harris greets attendees after speaking about the administrations efforts to lower prescription drug costs during an event at Prince Georges Community College in Largo, Md., Thursday, Aug. 15, 2024. (AP Photo/Susan Walsh)

Fans of singer Taylor Swift, called Swifties, arrive at Wembley Stadium in London, Thursday, Aug. 15, 2024 for the first of five concerts of Taylor Swifts Eras Tour.(AP Photo/Alastair Grant)

Esther Bote, 14, walks to school with her friends in a bushy area on the periphery of the Save Valley Conservancy in Zimbabwe, Tuesday, July 9, 2024. The conservancy and the countrys parks agency have been running a program for school-age children on how to recognize danger signs and how to coexist with wildlife. (AP Photo/Tsvangirayi Mukwazhi)
